    <h2>Introduction</h2>
    <p>Welcome to the Online Voting System. Your privacy is important to us, and we are committed to protecting the personal information you provide. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, store, and safeguard your data.</p>

    <h3>Information We Collect</h3>
    <p>We collect personal information such as name, email address, voter ID, and login credentials when you register or log in to the system. We also gather usage data like IP addresses and browser type for security and analytics purposes.</p>

    <h3>How We Use Your Information</h3>
    <p>Your data is used solely to authenticate users, manage elections, record votes securely, and enhance system performance. We do not share your information with third parties unless legally required.</p>

    <h3>Data Security</h3>
    <p>We implement strong security protocols including encryption, secure server hosting, and access controls to protect your information against unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure.</p>

    <h3>Cookies</h3>
    <p>Cookies are used to improve your experience on our website. These small data files help us remember your login session and enhance usability. You may disable cookies in your browser settings if preferred.</p>

    <h3>Third-Party Services</h3>
    <p>We do not use any third-party advertising or data-sharing services. However, external links (if any) may be governed by their respective privacy policies.</p>

    <h3>Your Rights</h3>
    <p>You have the right to access, update, or delete your personal information stored in our system. For any such requests, please contact our support team.</p>

    <h3>Policy Updates</h3>
    <p>This policy may be updated periodically. Any significant changes will be communicated to registered users via email or announcements within the platform.</p>

    <h3>Contact Us</h3>
    <p>If you have questions about this policy or our data practices, please <a href="#contact">contact us</a>.</p>
